Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.14,0:02:01.18,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:04.10,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:09.23,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,暗闇に浮かんだ　棚引く淡い光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:14.45,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,まだ見ぬ未知の陽は　誰を照らし出すの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.45,0:02:19.20,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,愛しき My Buddy　哀しみくれても Don't worry
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:24.17,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,何があっても　生き抜け That's all
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.17,0:02:26.46,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Mysterious…　さぁ手を伸ばせ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.46,0:02:28.84,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Cyber world…　この闇を抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.84,0:02:31.05,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Take your hands…　脈打つ鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.05,0:02:34.68,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Danger Danger Danger　飛び出せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:38.35,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,見つめる世界の果て
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:45.19,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,小さな胸に　憧れを　詰め込んだら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:55.11,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,琥珀の夢　約束のあの場所まで　いざ行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:03:02.50,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,キミを想う気持ちは　この空よりもでかい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:08.63,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,無限大　いつでも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.63,0:03:15.55,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:19.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
Comment: 0,0:01:54.14,0:02:01.18,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Comment: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:04.10,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:09.23,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,黯淡的光暈  浮現於黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:14.45,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,未見未知的陽光  會將誰照亮？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.45,0:02:19.20,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,我親愛的伙伴  就算沉浸於悲傷也不慌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:24.17,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,不管發生什麼事  活下去才是唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.17,0:02:26.46,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,Mysterious…  來伸出手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.46,0:02:28.84,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,Cyber world…  穿過這片黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.84,0:02:31.05,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,Take your hands…  衝擊全身的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.05,0:02:34.68,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,Danger Danger Danger  起飛吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:38.35,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,緊盯著世界的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:45.19,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,當小小胸膛填滿了憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:55.11,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,琥珀之夢  朝著約定的地點出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:03:02.50,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,對你的關心關愛  比這天空更寬廣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:08.63,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,無限擴張  永無止境
Comment: 0,0:03:08.63,0:03:15.55,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say…
Comment: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:19.43,OP-CHT,,0,0,0,,No matter what I say…
